{"tid":1280713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心「災後心理輔導中心」，疑似有紅色背景","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:06:01.000Z","uid":268459,"like":252,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b5b2e23d0c32a5abdc6758540d12d877492450","tid":1280713,"uid":268459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"剛剛聽到電台新聞報導，一個名為「災後心理輔導中心」的組織，自稱已介入輔導抗爭者，有點擔心有可疑，因為該機構之前曾經與建制背景的人合作，有抹黑反送中運動的嫌疑，甚至大公報也報導過該機構的「工作」，我恐怕這機構會以輔導為名，收集抗爭者資料為實，可否協助查證及廣傳一下，提醒各人小心留意，起碼要自己查清楚一下該機構的底勢。"},{"pid":"d91b1218af375cecdbde7a3812e54dcba53c324a","tid":1280713,"uid":268459,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"緊急!<br />\n<br />\n各位弟兄請留意, 不久前在電台聽到有一間名為:&quot;災後心理輔導中心&quot; 說可以向有需要人提供輔導.<br />\n<br />\n此機構為親建制組織, 有和教聯會合作, 多在&quot;頭條日報&quot;,&quot;星島日報&quot;等賣廣告, 服務地點隨香港外, 還在東亞, 東南亞, 和主力在大陸有服務.<br />\n<br />\n大家在求助時, 務必小心. 以免被&quot;督灰&quot;和出賣!"},{"pid":"86dffb196c47dbeca9b5e10246c509a17aaadefd","tid":1280713,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d693d2c51f679cadfded1bab03352b73dde7cc85","tid":1280713,"uid":261982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed430f839fe67961b14de242c85f23df6e95a0c","tid":1280713,"uid":261982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"推一推，搵人check下"},{"pid":"d7dd7e9f7ef683208376eef3204dedda134e0893","tid":1280713,"uid":193125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"推 係真的話 有唔少人已經奶野"},{"pid":"db1fcdfe056025d4c3c6ff78e5983a5fa5bf2e33","tid":1280713,"uid":161222,"like":11,"dislike